                        <button class="accordion">What is Visage?</button>
                        <div class="panel">
                            <p>Visage is your virtual sourcing team. Submit your job requirements and Visage delivers qualified candidates in just 24-hours. Engage your shortlisted candidates with custom messages via email.</p>
